entries.title: Musk Champions Twitter Fact-Checking Feature
entries.description: Community Notes, which uses an algorithm to combat false and misleading information, has corrected tweets from the new platform owner himself.

entries.title: The Children Making Millions on YouTube
entries.description: Vlad, Niki, Diana and Nastya party on yachts, ride in Ferraris and travel the world. Their massive audience of fellow kids can’t get enough.

entries.title: U.S. Expands Bans of Chinese Security Cameras, Network Equipment
entries.description: The Federal Communications Commission voted to ban sales of new telecom and surveillance equipment made by several Chinese companies, arguing that their ownership and practices threaten U.S. national security.
